### GET All Orders (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders

### Create New Order
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
content-type: application/json

{
    "isAdmin": true,
    "user": "68f5f80500964c6ea40e6012",
    "orderItems": [
        {
            "product": "68ecc2b44d49272f5636f322",
            "quantity": 1
        },
        {
            "product": "68f5f84400964c6ea40e6017",
            "quantity": 1
        }
    ]
}

